id=nh-logcatd
name=NetHunter Logcat Daemon v3.1 (Magisk ecosystem + SELinux observability)
version=v3.1
versionCode=31
author=ilyamen
description=12-layer logging for v1.1.1 kernel. Logcat 128MB rotating, 30s dmesg snapshots, all pstore types (dmesg/console/ftrace/pmsg-ramoops), AUTO-FREEZE panic incidents, boot history (50 boots), boot marker via /dev/pmsg0, Magisk daemon log + per-module status snapshot at every boot (module versions, disable/remove flags, post-fs/service.d scripts), SELinux AVC denials watcher (60s polling). Storage budget cap 600MB. Run `nh-collect-logs.sh` to bundle.
